{"lastModified":1775135091150,"uri":"c::10120242293::vessel::2440a6a0-f00a-11ee-a725-1dbe0af55ad7","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nWelcome aboard Lagoon 55 – Tri Wing, where luxury and innovation unite for an unparalleled sailing adventure. This exceptional catamaran sets new standards in design, performance, and comfort. Indulge in the ultimate maritime experience while equipped with an array of amenities. With 5 lavish guest cabins and two private peak cabins for the crew, every aspect of comfort and privacy is meticulously catered to.  \n\nMoreover, elevate your journey with an assortment of extras. Explore the serene waters atop stand-up paddleboards (SUP) or cast your line with top-of-the-line fishing gear. Immerse yourself in the vibrant underwater world sliding on inflatable slider or exploring underwater life by snorkeling gear we prepared for you, and as the sun sets, watch the ocean come to life with the enchanting glow of underwater lights—an extraordinary addition to enhance your sailing experience. \n\nFor more adventurous clients, it's good to know that TRI-WING is licensed to navigate in international waters, so special long-term charters could be arranged upon your requests. \n\nThe name \"Tri Wing\" is inspired by the Tri-Wing S-91x Pegasus Starfighter from Star Wars, symbolizing agility, speed, and futuristic design. It evokes a sense of power and high-performance, aligning with the yacht's sleek and dynamic capabilities.","blueprint":{"name":"TRI WING","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::2440a6a0-f00a-11ee-a725-1dbe0af55ad7::assets::df163e20-fdcb-11ef-bddd-9f4a89ff2750/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::2440a6a0-f00a-11ee-a725-1dbe0af55ad7::assets::df227320-fdcb-11ef-bdde-9f4a89ff2750/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::2440a6a0-f00a-11ee-a725-1dbe0af55ad7::assets::def066a1-fdcb-11ef-bddd-9f4a89ff2750/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::2440a6a0-f00a-11ee-